column4: UK's M&S  Microsoft sign artificial intelligence deal
column5: LONDON Britain's Marks & Spencer has signed a strategic partnership deal with Microsoft to test the integration of artificial intelligence technologies into the retailer's stores and operations  it said on Thursday.

column4: UPDATE 8-Intel CEO resigns after probe of relationship with employee
column5: June 21 Intel Corp Chief Executive Brian Krzanich resigned on Thursday after an investigation found he had a consensual relationship with an employee in breach of company policy.

column4: Intel CEO resigns after probe into relationship with employee
column5: June 21 Intel Corp on Thursday said Chief Executive Officer Brian Krzanich has resigned  effective immediately  after a probe revealed that a past consensual relationship with an Intel employee violated company policy.
